reviewText: This is a beautiful DVD of the rosary i have enjoyed my copy for a very long time and I've sent copies to my family and friends and they are very happy with it also

I am disappointed as this is advertised as a DVD... It is a CD... big difference.... I was expecting the same as the EWTN series with all the still shots and Mother Angelica Praying the Rosary with her sisters...
Terrific product.  Don't have cable so I can watch this any time I like.
